                    "text": "Labor Department of Chhattisgarh State started this scheme \"Asangathit Karmakar Gambhir Bimari Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana\" for unorganized worker on 28 April 2012. Under this scheme, financial assistance will be provided for the medical treatment of serious illness like treatment of kidney, cancer, sickle cell anemia, heart disease, AIDS and paralysis. "
                  }
